summary: Makes Whiterun a bit more beautiful!
descriptionHtml:
Changed a few things in Whiterun to make it a tad more beautiful.

New topcaps!
(Vanilla ones were too dirty for my taste and the normals were messed up.)

New maingate!
(Some stuff on the vanilla one had really bad textures, so I kind of fixed that up.)

New stonewalls!
(Tried to make them a bit more realistic and interesting.)

PLEASE NOTE:
This is my FIRST texture EVER. So please, tell me what you think!

READ_ME for more information.
author: KimonJ
